OL,3,CRough sleeper left with spinal
OL,4,Cinjuries in town centre attack
OL,6,FA homeless man was left with multiple
OL,7,Fbroken bones and a punctured lung
OL,8,Fafter a brutal attack by two men,
OL,9,Fpolice have said.
OL,11,FThe 50-year-old victim was assaulted
OL,12,Fin Pontefract town centre in West
OL,13,FYorkshire in March, suffering two
OL,14,Fspinal fractures and four fractured
OL,15,Fribs.
OL,17,FThe attack occurred on Market Place in
OL,18,Fthe early hours of Saturday, 14 March.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
