OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778868676
OL,3,CRough sleeper left with spinal
OL,4,Cinjuries in town centre attack
OL,6,FOne man has since been charged over
OL,7,Fthe attack, while detectives on Friday
OL,8,Freleased CCTV of another suspect they
OL,9,Fwant to find.
OL,11,FWest Yorkshire Police said anyone who
OL,12,Frecognised the man in the stills
OL,13,Fshould contact Wakefield CID.
OL,15,FJake Marshall, 31, of Heather Gardens
OL,16,Fin Pontefract, appeared at Leeds
OL,17,FMagistrates Court on Tuesday charged
OL,18,Fwith grievous bodily harm in
OL,19,Fconnection with the assault in March.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
