OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778868676
OL,3,CRough sleeper left with spinal
OL,4,Cinjuries in town centre attack
OL,6,FHe is also charged with a second
OL,7,Fincident of causing grievous bodily
OL,8,Fharm on Hardwick Road in the town
OL,9,Fearlier this month.
OL,11,FMarshall was remanded into custody in
OL,12,FTuesday's hearing and will next appear
OL,13,Fbefore Leeds Crown Court on 11 June.
